<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how Auto Insurance Management System collects, uses, and protects your personal information.</p>

<h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Personal details such as name, address, contact information, and vehicle details.</li>
    <li>Policy and claim information including claim history, uploaded documents, and payment records.</li>
    <li>Login and usage data for account security and system improvement.</li>
</ul>

<h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
<ul>
    <li>To manage your insurance policies and claims.</li>
    <li>To communicate important updates and notifications.</li>
    <li>To comply with legal and regulatory requirements.</li>
</ul>

<h4>3. Data Protection</h4>
<p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</p>

<h4>4. Sharing of Information</h4>
<p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with trusted partners for claim processing, fraud prevention, or legal compliance.</p>

<h4>5. Your Rights</h4>
<p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. Contact our support team for assistance.</p>

<h4>6. Changes to This Policy</h4>
<p>We may update this policy from time to time. Please review it periodically for any changes.</p>

<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@autoinsure.com">support@autoinsure.com</a>.</p>
